<br>
Make a gnome on your account of the same class as your main and name him turbomasterfx then go to the eq.ini file and type the following line in the file under the section of window positioning<br>
<br>
VIDQD<br>
<br>
This should activate god mode because I did this process and let me tell you my spells resisted LESS than they did before.<br>
<br>
Also on a side note I'm finding that it also helps if you delete DOS from your computer. Try it, I think I read way back a long time ago that it will help lessen your resist rates since they get stealth nerfed every patch.<br>
<br>
*EDIT* Oh oh one other trick I forgot. For the class on your server or maybe on any server, the percentile of the color of your robe for people wearing robes of your class dictates resists. So if you're a mage don't wear a red robe, because all mages have red robes. some have those green SMRs which will have slight resists, but not as bad as red. Get a gossamer robe and your resists should go down a lot further. <p><center><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=109465>~~~~Krilen !~~~~</a></center></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ukrilenspiritlink.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Krilen Spiritlink</A> at: 6/22/02 4:50:23 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uadonhiram.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Adonhiram</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 65<br> <font color=#333333>(6/22/02 5:28:42 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1361.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: ArchMage Spec: Evoke Sirroco vs. Spec: Conj SoFB</span><hr size=1> HTML Comments are not allowed <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uadonhiram.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Adonhiram</A> at: 6/22/02 5:29:12 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ubalanzsonofanz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Balanz son of Anz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Abuser of EZCodes</span><br>  Posts: 1550<br> <font color=#333333>(6/22/02 9:06:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1361.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top 